{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b25d2184fd","title":"致刘伯承、邓小平电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c85e15262b","index":0,"year":1947,"month":10,"day":8,"articleId":"b25d2184fd"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c5920e4b32","type":"paragraph","text":"致刘伯承、邓小平电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"b25d2184fd"},{"id":"911093cd91","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年10月8日）你们手里只有七个旅，不要再分散。现在不要出平汉及平汉以西。陈、谢环境很好，不须你们配合。你们按照自己情况，逐步克段困难，争取胜利。无把握的仅不要打。[I]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起尊的数刘伯承、邓小平屯的主要内容。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"b25d2184fd"}],"page":{"id":"d594b507bf","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"b25d2184fd","start":339,"end":339}}}},"__N_SSG":true}